com.w2.api.engine.operators

Class CommandSetSequenceFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w2.api.engine.operators.CommandSetSequenceFrame

  • public class CommandSetSequenceFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    The `CommandSetSequenceFrame` object is a container for a single `RobotCommandSet` object and its execution time (in seconds). This class is used in conjunction with the `CommandSetSequence` class to represent serial, ordered execution for WonderWorkshop robots.
